description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a motivated &lt;strong&gt;Clinical Team Leader (RMN/RNLD) &lt;/strong&gt;with a passion for delivering the best quality of care, to drive change, improve practice and be part of a hospital wide quality improvement project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;Male PICU and Male Autistic Spectrum Disorder (ASD).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary:&lt;/strong&gt;£35,169 to £40,449 per annum pro rata, with opportunity to earn up to £44,785 including enhancements&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours: &lt;/strong&gt;up to full time (38.5 hours per week)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cygnet Hospital Wyke&lt;/strong&gt; is transforming. Committed to delivering safe, effective, person-centred care, we are looking to recruit experienced &lt;strong&gt;Registered Mental Health Nurses (RMN)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Registered Learning Disability Nurses (RNLD)&lt;/strong&gt; who share our ambition to be outstanding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We value our colleagues and provide a comprehensive range of wellbeing and professional development activities including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Individual/group clinical supervision and de-briefing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trauma informed care and psychological formulation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leadership and coaching&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cognitive Behavioural Therapy, Dialectical Behaviour Therapy, Schema Therapy and EMDR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working closely with local universities, we are building a culture of clinical excellence with opportunities to undertake research in practice, evaluate latest evidence based interventions and deliver teaching/training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Cygnet? We’ll offer you…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS and employee discount scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;50% NMC registration renewal paid by Cygnet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free meals on duty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;RCNi membership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company paid Life Assurance scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Smart Health Toolkit- Providing you with Fitness Programmes, Nutrition consultation and Health checks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Next steps…&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Call us to find out more and discuss our exciting programme of development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You may like to visit, meet us and have a look around&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to make a positive change?&lt;/strong&gt; Please click on the ‘apply now’ link below.&lt;/p&gt;
